382→    <h1>Your personal agent activity&nbsp;feed</h1>
383→    <p class="subtitle">
384→      Not another orchestrator. A&nbsp;dashboard that makes sense of every session your AI agents have run — across repos, your home directory, notes, configs, everywhere.
385→    </p>
386→    <div class="title-meta">
387→      <span><span class="dot"></span> Open source &middot; Apache 2.0</span>
388→      <span><span class="dot"></span> pip install agent-kitchen</span>
389→      <span><span class="dot"></span> Zero config, zero workflow change</span>
390→    </div>
