395→<section class="slide" id="slide-2">
396→  <div class="slide-inner">
397→    <p class="kicker">The gap</p>
398→    <h2>Orchestrators assume your agent lives in a&nbsp;repo. Yours&nbsp;doesn't.</h2>
399→
400→    <div class="problem-grid">
401→      <div class="problem-col">
