409→          <span>Agents run in containers or worktrees — isolated from your machine context</span>
410→        </div>
411→        <div class="problem-item them">
412→          <span class="icon">C</span>
413→          <span>Must launch agents through their UI to get any visibility</span>
414→        </div>
415→        <div class="problem-item them">
416→          <span class="icon">C</span>
417→          <span>No view of non-repo work: dotfiles, notes, home&nbsp;directory&nbsp;tasks</span>
418→        </div>
419→      </div>
420→      <div class="problem-col">
421→        <h3>Agent Kitchen</h3>
422→        <div class="problem-item us">
423→          <span class="icon">AK</span>
424→          <span>Sessions grouped by repo <em>and</em> non-repo locations like ~/dotfiles, ~/notes</span>
425→        </div>
426→        <div class="problem-item us">
