446→    <p class="kicker">In action</p>
447→    <h2>See everything. Resume&nbsp;anything.</h2>
448→    <p class="subtitle" style="max-width: 55ch;">
449→      Browse sessions across repos and non-repo directories with AI summaries and git status — then resume any session right in the browser.
450→    </p>
